NameImport Shapes
ID3
AuthorO.Conrad (c) 2008

Description

The "OGR Vector Data Import" module imports vector data from various file/database formats using the "Geospatial Data Abstraction Library" (GDAL) by Frank Warmerdam. For more information have a look at the GDAL homepage: http://www.gdal.org GDAL Version:2.2.3 Following raster formats are currently supported:
